entries.original: The somehow magic-like superior performance of Factory Droids CLI
entries.translated: Factory Droids CLI의 마법 같은 뛰어난 성능

entries.original: The experience of AmpCode's excellent problem-solving ability and outstanding utilities (Oracle, Librarian, ...)
entries.translated: AmpCode의 뛰어난 문제 해결 능력과 훌륭한 유틸리티 경험 (Oracle, Librarian 등)

entries.original: The experience of Claude Code's rich features (asynchronous sub-agents, skills, etc.)
entries.translated: Claude Code의 풍부한 기능 경험 (비동기 하위 에이전트, 스킬 등)

entries.original: The experience of OpenCode's excellent TUI
I like 'OmO' because the letters look somewhat cute. I think it was named really well.
entries.translated: 'OmO'라는 이름이 글자가 귀여워 보여서 좋아합니다. 정말 잘 지은 이름이라고 생각합니다.

entries.original: OhMyOpenCode {version} will now appear as a toast when starting up.
Fixed the issue where all OpenCode caches were cleared during updates.
entries.translated: 중 모든 OpenCode 캐시가 지워지는 문제를 수정했습니다.
